:AntigoneMotivation_AffirmPietyBeforeDeath a :Motivation,
        owl:NamedIndividual ;
    :description "Antigone seeks to bear witness to her suffering and to frame it as the result of honoring piety (εὐσέβεια) as she is led away."^^xsd:string .

